{"tid":2312034,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［老豆劣作] 煮玻璃送烏東","createTime":"2020-12-04T13:58:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T04:32:12.000Z","uid":231089,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"285ac9bad3a03c89c0814d76bb6d129b7d50fbed","tid":2312034,"uid":231089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T13:58:51.000Z","msg":"今日晏晝我爸爸食淨左一碗湯烏冬<br />\n跟住佢放咗入雪櫃<br />\n佢夜晚應該係想煮返熱嚟食<br />\n<br />\n由於我哋屋企係冇微波爐<br />\n焗爐佢又懶得開 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢就將成個湯碗放入一煲熱水入面煲滾佢。<br />\n佢嚇到屋企個老人家都呆左<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ddwA11Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FddwA11Z.jpg&h=330c78ef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UDk6pfm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUDk6pfm.jpg&h=80e36b90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以後都唔想見到烏東...<br />\n邊有人將青瓜同蘿蔔放係烏東入面..<br />\n仲有無限玻璃...."},{"pid":"3048ca25688665f3e428af1f66b73b29a2d11b81","tid":2312034,"uid":24467,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T13:59:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"506d0acb408c183510dc45e75ea4f53d935ff310","tid":2312034,"uid":231089,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T13:59:33.000Z","msg":"係啊 我係開比你睇架老豆 拜託你檢討下<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇左個碗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d35883c952c55b330fb3394c1ab0b660f0a8a74e","tid":2312034,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T14:00:23.000Z","msg":"竟然無微波爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b87d60b8